                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-126-victim790 t18340703-126-viclabel695"></join>. On the 28th of May we lost this writing-desk from the door - I was looking through the window, and saw the prisoner take it - he put his apron over it, and walked about two hundred yards - I pursued, and took him with it.</p>
